sql.up: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS project  (id uuid   primary key   default (gen_random_uuid () )  not null  , title varchar (2048)  not null  , description text   not null  , tags json   default (('[]')::json ) , links json   default (('[]')::json ) , position integer   default (0)  not null  , "categoryId" uuid  , "thumbnailId" uuid  , visibility "visibility"   default ('draft')  not null  )
